6/29/83 forum request: lastref, lref

Syntax:  lref {trans_spec} {-control_args}


Syntax as an active request:  [lref {trans_spec} {-control_args}]


Function:
Prints or returns the transaction index of the last transaction in the
same chain as the specified transaction, or in the same chain as the
current transaction if no trans_spec is given.


Arguments:
trans_spec
   is the transaction for which the lastref is desired.


Control arguments:
-include_deleted, -idl
   print or return the index of the last transaction in the chain even
   if it is deleted.
-only_deleted, -odl
   print or return the index of the last deleted transaction in the chain.
-only_non_deleted, -ondl
   print or return the index of the last non-deleted transaction in the.
   chain. (Default)
